videos.description: Alexander Mattison follows his blocks for the easy 4-yard touchdown to put the Broncos on the board early.
videos.headline: Boise State's Mattison  runs up the middle for TD

videos.description: Tyler Horton jumps the route and gets the interception to stop Washington State's opening drive.
videos.headline: Boise State's Horton gets the INT in the red zone

videos.description: Boise State's Brett Rypien gets sacked, loses the ball and Robert Taylor picks up the live ball  and returns it for the score.
videos.headline: Washington State's defense forces the fumble and returns it for TD

videos.description: Frankie Luvu comes free and gets the sack with authority on Boise State's Brett Rypien.
videos.headline: Washington State's Luvu comes unblocked and delivers huge hit

videos.description: Washington State's Mike Leach is not happy with his team offensive effort in the first half.
videos.headline: Frustrated Leach stays succinct at the half

videos.description: Montell Cozart with the great pass to Cedrick Wilson who goes up and gets it for a 47-yard gain.
videos.headline: Boise State's Wilson rises up for the nice jumping catch

videos.description: Alexander Mattison makes the grab, gets  hit right away and fumbles the ball recovered by Marcellus Pippins of Washington State.
videos.headline: Washington State forces a fumble inside their own 5-yard line

videos.description: Montell Cozart scrambles and runs over a defender for a 14-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Boise State's Cozart powers in for TD run

videos.description: Washington State's Tyler Hilinski pass gets deflected and intercepted by Durrant Miles.
videos.headline: Boise State gets INT off tipped pass

videos.description: Montell Cozart finds Cedrick Wilson down the field for a 47-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Boise State's Wilson makes the grab for long TD

videos.description: Washington State's Luke Falk feels the pressure, gets hit and Curtis Weaver gets the interception and returns it all the way for a Boise State touchdown.
videos.headline: Boise State puts pressure on the QB and gets the pick-6

videos.description: Tyler Hillnski finds an uncovered Jamire Calvin for a 17-yard touchdown for the Cougars.
videos.headline: Washington State's Calvin is wide up and makes TD catch

videos.description: Montell Cozart tries to do too much and his pass is intercepted by Peyton Pelluer who returns it to the house for their 2nd defensive touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Washington State's defense forces the pick-6

videos.description: On the punt the ball bounces off Boise State's Reid Harrison-Ducros and is recovered by Dillon Sherman of Washingotn State deep in their territory.
videos.headline: Washington State recovers fumble off their own punt

videos.description: Tyler Hillinski passes it to Jamal Morrow who walks in for the touchdown to complete the 21-point comeback for the Cougars.
videos.headline: Washington State's Morrow TD ties game late in 4th Quarter

videos.description: Gerard Wicks lowers the shoulder and scores the touchdown in the second overtime.
videos.headline: Washington State's Wicks powers in for TD in 2nd OT

videos.description: Montell Cozart finds Cedrick Wilson over the middle for the touchdown in the second overtime.
videos.headline: Boise State's Wilson catches the TD to force 3rd OT

videos.description: Washington State coach Mike Leach is happy with the way his team fought and how his Quaterback Tyler Hillsnki stepped up in the triple-overtime win.
videos.headline: Leach happy with how everyone on the team contributed

videos.description: Rod Gilmore and Kevin Brown break down the crazy and epic comeback by the Cougars over the Broncos.
videos.headline: Break down of the wild comeback win by Washington State
